Rest assured that you Nasir Gebelli fans will not be disappointed by this one!"<ref name="callamaras198112">{{cite news | url=https://archive.org/stream/byte-magazine-1981-12/1981_12_BYTE_06-12_Computer_Games#page/n91/mode/2up | title=Gorgon | work=BYTE | date=December 1981 | accessdate=19 October 2013 | author=Callamaras, Peter V | pages=90}}</ref>

